Package org.eclipse.papyrus.arrowhead.profile.arrowheadsysmlprofile

Interface SystemRegistryForm

All Superinterfaces:
DataSemantics, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
SystemRegistryFormImpl
public interface SystemRegistryForm extends DataSemantics
A representation of the model object 'System Registry Form'.

The following features are supported:

  • System Name
  • Host Device
  • Authentication Info
  • End Of Validity
  • Service URI
  • Version
  • Deploy Time
  • Metadata1
  • Metadata2
See Also:
  • ArrowheadSysMLProfilePackage.getSystemRegistryForm()
